____________________________________________________________________FIND NUMBER OF DIVISORS USING PRIME FACTORIZATION_________________________________________________________________________

Kuno ekta number er number of divisor holo oi number er prime divisor er jei power gula ache oigula use kore joto dula different combinator toiri kora jay .

12 = pow(2,2) * pow(3,1) -------------------> NumberOfDivisors = (2+1) * (1+1) = 3 * 2 = 6 .

Normally number of divisor ber korte amra je loop chaliye iterate kori sqrt(n) porjonto oi algorithm er time complexity holo O(sqrt(n)) . Kintu prime factorization
er maddhome number of divisor ber korle er complexity hoy O( sqrt(n) / log(sqrt(n)) ) . Onekta time complexity kome jay eivabe number of divisor ber korle .
